{"tid":1661076,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地漢紅磡買黃金被騙逾500萬元","createTime":"2019-10-18T01:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T02:38:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1d5da2512f6984f9aa2016c94559b629c4a44c4c","tid":1661076,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:43:14.000Z","msg":"一名內地男子昨晚在紅磡買黃金，被人騙去大約560萬元，警方正追緝一名涉案男子。<br />\n警方昨晚7時許接報，37歲事主表示在馬頭圍道37至39號一間樓上店舖，以560萬元現金購買黃金，一名年約50歲男子將該筆錢放入夾萬之後，並無將黃金交給事主，並失去蹤影，事主報警，警員到場發現夾萬內的現金不見了，估計有人由夾萬的另一對門取走現金，案件暫列以欺騙手段取得財產。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%BC%A2%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E8%B2%B7%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%99%E9%80%BE500%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-224137184.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E7%25B4%2585%25E7%25A3%25A1%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E9%25BB%2583%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A8%2599%25E9%2580%25BE500%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-224137184.html&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizyfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=33a9be68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%BC%A2%E7%B4%85%E7%A3%A1%E8%B2%B7%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E8%A2%AB%E9%A8%99%E9%80%BE500%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-224137184.html</a>"},{"pid":"3371fb76949320660343b68e29b5c8c98eda801b","tid":1661076,"uid":122343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"左手交右手啫"},{"pid":"af08d9f86575ef1042f7f35ac8e25d75955c1ad0","tid":1661076,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:46:15.000Z","msg":"1018面具<br />\n1020 九龍"},{"pid":"85fcfd06b94c0e8fa1b612e9b54cd4cf3ba1fbd0","tid":1661076,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T02:38:05.000Z","msg":"自己友"}]}